{
  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Abzeeck flaht juhs Pa-\ngani klausijht / un juhs\nTautas jemmet weh-\nrā / lat ta Semme klaufa / un\nkas us to irraid/ ta Paſaule / un\nwiſs kas no tahs ſanga.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo ta KUNGA Apſai-\nſchana irr pahr wiſſeim Paga-\nxeem/ un Bahrsiba pahr wiſſu\nwinno Spehku / wiſſch iſdel-\ndebs tohs / un nodohs tohs us\nRaufchanu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un winno Nokautee taps\natneſti/ un no winnu nomirru-\nſchahn Meeſahm uſkahps nikna\nSmarſcha/ un tee Kalni iſkufs-\nfibs no winnu Affinim.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un wiſſ Debbeſchu Spehks\niſgindihs / un tahs Debbeſis\ntaps fatihtas ka weena Grahmata/ un wiſs winnu Spehke\nnoqurs/ itt ka Lappa famihst pee\nWihna-Rohka/ un ka ta famihſt\npee Wihges-Rohka.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo mans Sohbins irr\npeedſehris tappis Debbeſis/ rau-\ngi/ tas nolaideſees us Sohdibu\npahr Eedomu/ un pahr teem\nLandim/ fo es iſdeldeschnu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta KUNGA Sohbins irr\npils Affinu/ tas irr reſnis tap-\npis no Tankeem/ no to Zehru un\nAhſchu Affinim / no to Annu\nIheſio Tankeem: Jo tam KUN-\nGAN irr Raufchana Bozra / un teela Nokaufchana eekſch Ee-\ndoma Seunnes.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad taps tee Weenradſchi\nar wiſſeem paſemmoti/ un tee\nuni Wehrſchi ar teem iſbarro-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo iſht buhs ta Deen\ntahs leclas Atreepſchanas\nKUNGA / weens Gads tal\nAtmaſſafchanas/ Zianas Teeſ-\nſchanas deht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un winnas Uppes pah\nwehrtifees par Darwu/ un win-\nnas Pihschli par Schrahm /\nwinnas Semme taps par de\ngofchu Darwu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Neds Nafti nedg Deen\ntaps ta iſdſehsta / bet winnu\nDuhmi nekahps muhſchigi/lib\nZilſchu Ziltim buhs winnu po-\nſta/ ne weens ees zaur win-\nmuhſchigi muhſcham.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet tas Drumpis un t\nEfis winnu eenantohs / un\nPubza un Kranklis eekſch ta-\ndiſhwohs/ jo wiſſch wilks wee-\nMiehra-Aukli pahr winnu/ ka\npohſta paleek/ un Mehra-Akni/ ka ta tuſcha paleek.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tee gan taps Zeeni-\nnoſankti/ bet teem ne buhs\nkahdas Wallſibas/ un wiſſi w-\nras Peel-Kungi buhs par\nneeka.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un winnas ſkaistos Ma-\nmōs uſdihs Chriſchki / Ma-\ntres un Dadschi eekſch win-\nPillimi/ un winna buhs wee-\nMahjas-Weeta to Putku/\nweens Bagalns preekſch je-\nneem Strauteem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tee Svochri tahs Tu-\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
